<h3>Accordion</h3>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <p>Wrap a list of panels in a <code>cp-panels</code> component with <code>accordion=true</code>:</p>
    <p>
<pre>&lbrace;&lbrace;#cp-panels accordion=true&rbrace;&rbrace;
  &lbrace;&lbrace;#cp-panel&rbrace;&rbrace;
    &lbrace;&lbrace;#cp-panel-toggle&rbrace;&rbrace;
      Panel A
    &lbrace;&lbrace;/cp-panel-toggle&rbrace;&rbrace;
    &lbrace;&lbrace;cp-panel-body&rbrace;&rbrace;
      ...
    &lbrace;&lbrace;/cp-panel-body&rbrace;&rbrace;
  &lbrace;&lbrace;/cp-panel&rbrace;&rbrace;
  &lbrace;&lbrace;#cp-panel&rbrace;&rbrace;
    &lbrace;&lbrace;#cp-panel-toggle&rbrace;&rbrace;
      Panel B
    &lbrace;&lbrace;/cp-panel-toggle&rbrace;&rbrace;
    &lbrace;&lbrace;cp-panel-body&rbrace;&rbrace;
      ...
    &lbrace;&lbrace;/cp-panel-body&rbrace;&rbrace;
  &lbrace;&lbrace;/cp-panel&rbrace;&rbrace;
&lbrace;&lbrace;/cp-panels&rbrace;&rbrace;
</pre>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    {{#cp-panels accordion=true}}
      {{#cp-panel}}
        {{#cp-panel-toggle}}
          <p>Panel A</p>
        {{/cp-panel-toggle}}
        {{#cp-panel-body}}
